If you want your class properties to be dynamic, you can do that in `__construct` which is called automatically when you create a object of the class.


````
class Test {
 public $code = &#39;111&#39;;
 public $commands = [];
    
    public function __construct() {
		$this-&gt;commands[$this-&gt;code] = &quot;тест&quot;;
	}
}

$a = new Test();
var_dump( $a );
````

